Overview This project automates the extraction and synchronization of data from Okendo to Segment. It supports both historical backfills and daily incremental syncs, ensuring that Segment always has the latest customer review data from Okendo.

Features Backfill: Load historical reviews and data from Okendo into Segment.

Daily Sync: Automatically sync new reviews and updates every day.

Error Handling: Robust logging and error management for reliable data transfer.

Configurable: Set up with environment variables for API keys and scheduling.

Technologies Language: JavaScript (Node.js)

Integrations: Okendo API, Segment API
